#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.259"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.259:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.259:0.2"
msgid "26. Abhiññāvagga"
msgstr "26. Insight"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.259:0.3"
msgid "259. Paṭhamaājānīyasutta"
msgstr "259. A Thoroughbred (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.250"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.259:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūhi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato rañño bhadro assājānīyo rājāraho hoti "
"rājabhoggo, rañño aṅganteva saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a fine royal thoroughbred with four factors is worthy of a "
"king, fit to serve a king, and considered a factor of kingship."

msgctxt "an4.259:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.259:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, rañño bhadro assājānīyo vaṇṇasampanno ca hoti balasampanno "
"ca javasampanno ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a fine royal thoroughbred is beautiful, strong, fast, and well-"
"proportioned."

msgctxt "an4.259:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi aṅgehi samannāgato rañño bhadro assājānīyo "
"rājāraho hoti rājabhoggo, rañño aṅganteva saṅkhaṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"A fine royal thoroughbred with these four factors is worthy of a king. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.259:2.1"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu āhuneyyo hoti … "
"pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant with four factors is worthy of offerings "
"dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a teacher’s "
"offering, worthy of veneration with joined palms, and is a supreme field of "
"merit for the world."

msgctxt "an4.259:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.259:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vaṇṇasampanno ca hoti balasampanno ca javasampanno "
"ca ārohapariṇāhasampanno ca."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant is beautiful, strong, fast, and well proportioned."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.259:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vaṇṇasampanno hoti?"
msgstr "And how is a mendicant beautiful?"

msgctxt "an4.259:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlavā hoti … pe … samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant is ethical, restrained in the code of conduct, and has "
"appropriate behavior and means of collecting alms. Seeing danger in the "
"slightest flaw, they keep the rules they’ve undertaken."

msgctxt "an4.259:3.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vaṇṇasampanno hoti."
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant is beautiful."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.259:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu balasampanno hoti?"
msgstr "And how is a mendicant strong?"

msgctxt "an4.259:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu āraddhavīriyo viharati akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"pahānāya, kusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ upasampadāya, thāmavā daḷhaparakkamo "
"anikkhittadhuro kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant lives with energy roused up for giving up unskillful "
"qualities and gaining skillful qualities. They are strong, firmly applied, "
"not slacking off when it comes to developing skillful qualities."

msgctxt "an4.259:4.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu balasampanno hoti."
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant is strong."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.259:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu javasampanno hoti?"
msgstr "And how is a mendicant fast?"

msgctxt "an4.259:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when they truly understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin "
"of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice "
"that leads to the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "an4.259:5.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu javasampanno hoti."
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant is fast."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.251"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.259:6.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ārohapariṇāhasampanno hoti?"
msgstr "And how is a mendicant well proportioned?"

msgctxt "an4.259:6.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu lābhī hoti "
"cīvarapiṇḍapātasenāsanagilānapaccayabhesajjaparikkhārānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant receives robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and "
"supplies for the sick."

msgctxt "an4.259:6.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ārohapariṇāhasampanno hoti."
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant is well proportioned."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.259:7.1"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu āhuneyyo hoti … pe "
"… anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these four factors … is a supreme field of merit for the "
"world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.259:7.2"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
